title: EBOOT collection (PSX2PSP) - 36 PlayStation games
description:
36 PlayStation games converted to EBOOT format and playable (tested OK) in a PSP running 6.60 PRO-C2 CFW and/or with ePSXe-Win.

All games are NTSC except Alundra, Bishi Bashi Special, King's Field, The Granstream Saga and Warcraft II which are PAL.
